{"tid":2001191,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"超級區議會 泛民達共識搞初選","createTime":"2020-05-04T11:04:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-06T06:51:25.000Z","uid":134071,"like":46,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"2d1c45e8d73df40cfc91f985366f072080d81d98","tid":2001191,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T11:04:56.000Z","msg":"2020年4月30日<br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】民主派立法會選舉嘅協調工作如火如荼，前晚就舉行「超級區議會」界別嘅協調會議，據了解，會上至少有7個政團或有興趣人士出席會議。會議似乎幾順利，大家初步都認同要搞初選，暫傾向喺初選時，每名市民可以有4票，選出4隊泛民人馬。超區界別有5席，過去兩屆選舉都係民主派取3席、建制派取兩席。<br />\n民主黨、公民黨、社民連、新同盟，素人如荃灣區議員岑敖暉同南區區議員司馬文等都有出席會議。據悉會議達成初選嘅共識，會上大家另一關注點係被DQ嘅問題，故都有討論Plan B點運作。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/港聞/article/20200430/s00002/1588184865800/【emily】開會協調超區-泛民達共識搞初選\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20200430%2Fs00002%2F1588184865800%2F%E3%80%90emily%E3%80%91%E9%96%8B%E6%9C%83%E5%8D%94%E8%AA%BF%E8%B6%85%E5%8D%80-%E6%B3%9B%E6%B0%91%E9%81%94%E5%85%B1%E8%AD%98%E6%90%9E%E5%88%9D%E9%81%B8&d=QLsQNhMpkN58D9M0TNJg1vilxGv0e2UEk%2F7kpEYl8nk%3D&h=87748df2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20200430%2Fs00002%2F1588184865800%2F%E3%80%90emily%E3%80%91%E9%96%8B%E6%9C%83%E5%8D%94%E8%AA%BF%E8%B6%85%E5%8D%80-%E6%B3%9B%E6%B0%91%E9%81%94%E5%85%B1%E8%AD%98%E6%90%9E%E5%88%9D%E9%81%B8&h=941f6aa4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/港聞/article/20200430/s00002/1588184865800/【emily】開會協調超區-泛民達共識搞初選</a>"},{"pid":"d1940e4534fbaa6e5eca0b61a049481d21e45578","tid":2001191,"uid":134071,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T11:05:21.000Z","msg":"初選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48d526a552f26e93ba33c3f84e2f76259a80b06a","tid":2001191,"uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T11:06:50.000Z","msg":"支持初選"},{"pid":"1a78d291c4d7458675f8